Start the API and check that your source appears in the missions list:fornax-cutouts api
curl http://localhost:8000/api/v0/missions

Expected response includes your mission:{
  "my_mission": {
    "name": "my_mission",
    "pixel_size": 0.5,
    "max_cutout_size": 2000,
    "filter": ["g", "r", "i"],
    "survey": ["wide"]
  }
}
